[l] Das FBI kann keinen einzigen Terrorfall nennen, den sie wegen der Patriot-Act-Schnueffelbefugnisse geloest haetten.Inspector General Michael E. Horowitz said that between 2004 and 2009, the FBI tripled its use of bulk collection under Section 215 of the Patriot Act, which allows government agents to compel businesses to turn over records and documents, and increasingly scooped up records of Americans who had no ties to official terrorism investigations.Wie immer halt. Wo ein Trog ist, sammeln sich die Schweine.
